WEBVTT

00:00.022 --> 00:01.567
Previously on
"Devious Maids"...

00:02.291 --> 00:04.295
- What's that on your back seat?
- Nothing.

00:04.559 --> 00:07.266
Is that blood? Miss, you're
gonna have to come with me.

00:07.428 --> 00:10.896
- Who did you kill, Nick?
- I'm not a murderer.

00:10.898 --> 00:13.365
