I won't be there.

00:13.367 --> 00:14.933
I know what you're doing.

00:14.935 --> 00:16.335
If... if...

00:16.337 --> 00:17.703
If you will just give me
a chance to explain...

00:17.705 --> 00:19.905
Give me my cane.

00:19.907 --> 00:21.607
Mr. Kenneth?

00:21.609 --> 00:23.575
- Uncle Ken had a fall.
- What?

00:23.577 --> 00:24.943
She took my kid.

00:24.945 --> 00:26.745
Drinking won't get him back.

00:26.747 --> 00:28.947
I'll get my act together.
I promise.

00:31.284 --> 00:32.417
I know
you're sleeping with Tony.

00:32.418 --> 00:33.719
Tony makes me happy.

00:33.721 --> 00:35.253
Her husband has found out
about the affair.

00:35.255 --> 00:36.954
I just have to come up
with a new plan.

00:36.956 --> 00:39.257
When I knew him,
his name wasn't Tony.

00:39.259 --> 00:41.092
You must tell me more.

00:45.631 --> 00:48.433
Your bodyguard's real name
is Amir Hassan,

00:48.435 --> 00:51.536
but he's gone by
half a dozen different aliases.

00:51.538 --> 00:54.605
He is a con man with a record
as long as your yacht.

00:54.607 --> 00:56.941
Fraud, forgery, assault...

00:56.943 --> 00:59.710
Who says there are
no more renaissance men?

00:59.712 --> 01:01.278
His usual racket

01:01.280 --> 01:03.614
is to target wealthy,
middle-aged married women.

01:03.616 --> 01:06.784
He lures them into an affair,
and then blackmails them

01:06.786 --> 01:08.552
by threatening
to tell their husbands.

01:08.554 --> 01:11.721
Evelyn will be devastated
when she finds out.

01:11.723 --> 01:13.657
I can't wait to tell her.

01:14.635 --> 01:15.459
Thanks again, Rick.

01:15.461 --> 01:17.594
Let me know if there's
anything else I can do for you.

01:17.596 --> 01:19.929
Wait.

01:19.931 --> 01:22.299
