they're involved.

01:22.301 --> 01:23.967
Tony knows I know.

01:23.969 --> 01:25.636
- He does?
- Yes.

01:25.638 --> 01:28.138
So how can he possibly think
he's going to blackmail her?

01:28.140 --> 01:29.973
He must have thought
of some other way

01:29.975 --> 01:31.307
to get money out of you.

01:31.509 --> 01:33.843
But how?

01:38.349 --> 01:40.816
Hello, you.

01:40.818 --> 01:42.518
Good morning,
Mrs. Powell.

01:42.520 --> 01:46.288
