04:23.376 --> 04:25.343
He's got me in the mood.

04:25.345 --> 04:26.844
Well,
I will not sleep with him.

04:26.846 --> 04:28.178
He's a worm.

04:28.180 --> 04:29.513
A worm that paid
for a platinum setting.

04:29.515 --> 04:30.881
Carmen!

04:30.883 --> 04:32.182
Okay, I'll shut up
if I get to wear it.

04:32.184 --> 04:35.019
So, why do you think
Reggie is a worm?

04:35.021 --> 04:38.188
He got Mr. Kenneth to kick
his daughter out of the house,

04:38.190 --> 04:39.523
and then his wife.

04:39.525 --> 04:41.391
And now Mr. Kenneth
is in the hospital

04:41.393 --> 04:43.226
because of a "mysterious" fall.

04:43.228 --> 04:46.029
Why would Reggie
want to hurt his Uncle?

04:46.031 --> 04:48.198
He's embezzling
Mr. Kenneth's money.

04:48.200 --> 04:50.833
And with everybody gone,
he can get away with it.

04:50.835 --> 04:52.369
Maybe you should
call the police.

04:52.371 --> 04:55.205
I will once I have proof.

04:55.207 --> 04:56.706
How are you going to get that?

04:56.708 --> 04:59.543
I'll go through
Reggie's papers.

04:59.545 --> 05:01.177
If I can find copies

05:01.179 --> 05:04.714
of his bank statements
or wire transfers...

05:04.716 --> 05:07.183
Well, just don't let him know
that you're on to him.

05:07.185 --> 05:10.519
He doesn't think I'm smart
enough to figure this out.

05:10.521 --> 05:13.056
He just sees me
as some dumb immigrant.

05:13.058 --> 05:14.891
Then he is in
for a rude awakening.

05:14.893 --> 05:16.559
Well, I should get going.

05:16.561 --> 05:18.727
