we're about to be caught.

05:57.200 --> 05:58.933
Did you tell someone?

05:58.935 --> 06:00.868
Valentina.

06:00.870 --> 06:02.103
How could you do that?!

06:02.105 --> 06:04.939
I got stabbed,
and she's not stupid!

06:04.941 --> 06:06.241
This is bad.

06:06.243 --> 06:09.243
- I mean, if she tells someone...
- I don't think she will.

06:09.245 --> 06:10.444
But I'm getting out
just in case.

06:10.446 --> 06:11.646
You might want to do the same.

06:19.404 --> 06:20.621
Remi!

06:20.623 --> 06:22.456
Where is she?

06:22.458 --> 06:24.291
She's in some room
being questioned.

06:24.293 --> 06:25.459
They won't let me see her.

06:25.461 --> 06:26.793
Oh, my God.

06:26.795 --> 06:28.061
She didn't want me
to call you guys,

06:28.063 --> 06:29.329
but I didn't know
what else to do.

06:29.331 --> 06:30.631
Well, you did the right thing.

06:30.633 --> 06:31.665
I don't understand.

06:31.667 --> 06:33.133
Do you know what happened?

06:34.936 --> 06:36.537
You'll have to ask her.

06:40.975 --> 06:42.275
Mami!

06:42.277 --> 06:43.609
Mija!

06:43.611 --> 06:44.811
What's going on?

06:44.813 --> 06:46.646
They said they found blood
in your car.

06:46.648 --> 06:49.082
I know it looks bad, but I didn't
do anything wrong. I swear.

06:49.084 --> 06:50.817
We're willing
to believe her

06:50.819 --> 06:52.986
if she tells us whose blood
it is and how it got there.

06:52.988 --> 06:54.320
