06:56.191 --> 06:57.690
Valentina Josefina Diaz,

06:57.692 --> 06:59.825
you tell these people
what they want to know now.

06:59.827 --> 07:03.162
Can't we talk about it at home?

07:03.164 --> 07:04.664
First she has to answer
our questions.

07:04.666 --> 07:07.333
Wait a minute. Has she
been placed under arrest?

07:07.335 --> 07:09.535
