asked for.

08:05.558 --> 08:07.558
You and Miguel
are literally days away

08:07.560 --> 08:09.059
from getting resident status.

08:10.896 --> 08:12.730
Isn't that great?

08:12.732 --> 08:15.699
Yes. It is.

08:15.701 --> 08:18.235
Thank you so much
for all your hard work.

08:18.237 --> 08:20.070
It's my pleasure.

08:20.072 --> 08:22.372
What is this?

08:22.374 --> 08:24.241
Where did you get that?

08:24.243 --> 08:27.043
I found it on the floor.

08:27.045 --> 08:30.580
Oh.

08:30.582 --> 08:32.414
That's a brochure
for maple park.

08:32.417 --> 08:34.751
Best assisted-living center
in the country.

08:34.753 --> 08:38.254
They have pools,
uh, tennis courts, the works.

08:38.256 --> 08:39.722
Why would you have this?

08:39.724 --> 08:41.357
Well, after his fall,

08:41.359 --> 08:43.092
Uncle Ken will need more help
than we can provide.

08:43.094 --> 08:45.928
And maple park
has 24-hour medical care.

08:45.930 --> 08:48.063
But this is in Sacramento.

08:48.065 --> 08:49.766
How could we visit him?

08:49.768 --> 08:51.601
I'm sure we'd find a way.

08:51.603 --> 08:53.936
Look, the paperwork
has been signed.

08:53.938 --> 08:56.438
There's no point
in arguing about it.

08:56.440 --> 08:58.274
So, when are you
sending him there?

08:58.276 --> 09:00.575
Two weeks.

09:00.577 --> 09:02.244
No!

09:02.246 --> 09:05.114
Why are you getting so upset?

09:05.116 --> 09:07.283
My Uncle's going to be
well cared for.

09:07.285 --> 09:09.117
You're gonna get a green card.

09:09.119 --> 09:11.820
Come on, Rosie.

09:11.822 --> 09:14.323
It's a happy ending
for everyone.

09:20.072 --> 09:22.739
- Son of a bitch!
- What's wrong?

09:22.841 --> 09:26.176
Those idiotic writers... they've
