gonna be so upset.

09:30.348 --> 09:31.615
You know why they did it?

09:31.617 --> 09:33.082
So they can give
more screen time

09:33.084 --> 09:34.518
to that punk
playing Dr. Blake.

09:34.520 --> 09:36.753
Oh, he's so dreamy.

09:37.788 --> 09:39.623
For a punk.

09:39.625 --> 09:40.790
