Chinese takeout

10:46.990 --> 10:48.089
and I wouldn't have cared.

10:48.391 --> 10:50.824
So you began an affair.

10:50.826 --> 10:53.660
I'm not a stupid woman,
Mr. Powell.

10:53.662 --> 10:56.997
But he knew
all the right buttons to push.

10:56.999 --> 10:59.500
That is his talent.

10:59.502 --> 11:02.068
That's why I hate him.

11:02.070 --> 11:05.839
Mr. Hassan ended up
soaking Mrs. Parker for $80,000.

11:05.841 --> 11:10.676
