my husband unexpectedly died.

11:10.678 --> 11:13.179
Without that leverage...

11:13.181 --> 11:15.648
I'm so sorry.

11:18.152 --> 11:19.652
If I may ask...

11:19.654 --> 11:22.822
Are you going to tell your wife
what you've learned?

11:22.824 --> 11:24.757
How can I not?

11:24.759 --> 11:27.927
I suppose you have no choice.

11:27.929 --> 11:32.031
But I implore you
to proceed carefully.

11:33.700 --> 11:38.538
Women need
to feel beautiful and loved,

11:38.540 --> 11:40.673
