of a certain age.

11:40.675 --> 11:46.378
And when we discover
that we've been fools...

11:46.380 --> 11:51.850
It can break us
in ways men can't imagine.

12:00.861 --> 12:03.327
How can I help you, detectives?

12:03.329 --> 12:04.796
We're trying
to build a time line

12:04.798 --> 12:06.565
for the night
of your husband's accident.

12:06.567 --> 12:08.800
Do you know when he left
the house to go for his run?

12:08.802 --> 12:11.069
I was in bed reading,
and I fell asleep.

12:11.071 --> 12:12.571
Can't Nick tell you?

12:12.573 --> 12:15.139
He doesn't remember much,
which isn't surprising.

12:15.141 --> 12:16.740
I wish I could be more helpful.

12:16.742 --> 12:18.076
This is a big property.

12:18.078 --> 12:19.310
Do you have security cameras?

12:19.312 --> 12:20.778
We do.

12:26.085 --> 12:29.253
That's the end of the driveway,
by the front gate.

12:29.255 --> 12:30.421
9:05 P.M.

12:30.423 --> 12:33.223
Thank you,
Mrs. Deering.

12:33.225 --> 12:37.595
Please don't hesitate to call
if you have any other questions.

12:37.597 --> 12:39.262
I have one.

12:39.264 --> 12:41.732
Can you think of anyone who
would want to hurt your husband?

12:41.734 --> 12:43.500
What?

12:43.502 --> 12:45.769
