what to say.

13:39.990 --> 13:41.289
Well, for starters,

13:41.291 --> 13:42.991
why don't you tell me
what your "plan b" is.

13:42.993 --> 13:44.492
My plan "b"?

13:44.494 --> 13:46.628
Historically, you like
to blackmail your victims,

13:46.630 --> 13:48.496
threatening to expose
their tawdry affairs,

13:48.498 --> 13:51.499
but clearly, that won't work
with Evelyn and I.

13:51.501 --> 13:53.501
So I'm just dying to know...

13:53.503 --> 13:55.403
What is your next move?

13:57.406 --> 14:00.808
I intend to file a lawsuit.

14:00.810 --> 14:02.577
