What kind of lawsuit?

14:02.579 --> 14:04.145
For harassment.

14:04.147 --> 14:08.183
Your wife forced me
to perform sexual acts

14:08.185 --> 14:12.352
and threatened to fire me
if I failed to comply.

14:12.354 --> 14:14.321
I have a recording.

14:18.359 --> 14:20.227
Is that
what I found in your clock?

14:22.998 --> 14:24.531
